      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The specials placed on\nduty at the instance of the\nW. w. p. Co. are certain to\ncause serious trouble unless\ntheir indiscriminate arrests\nOf anybody in sight when\nthe cry \"scab\" Is raised,\nare stopped and the police\npowers reIeoated to the\nproper authorities. The ac-\nton of inexperienced spe-\nGals, new to authority and\nlacking in judgment, is\nbrewing a current Of bitter\nness that will be hard to\ncontrol IL this abuse of\npower is permitted to con-\ntinue.\n\n\nIt is the duty Of the city\nauthorities to prevent in\nfractions of this nature as\nwe'll as any possible violence.\n0OOC00SSOOSOO0"
